Database Design
Documents Collection:

document_id: Unique identifier.
title: Document title.
content: The actual content of the document.
versions: Array of document versions for version control.
created_by: User who created the document.
collaborators: List of users who can edit the document.
Users Collection:

user_id: Unique identifier.
username: Username for login.
password_hash: Hashed password for authentication.
documents: Array of document IDs the user has access to.
